{{zh-forms|[[身在曹营心在汉]]|[[身]][[在]][[曹]][[營]][[心]][[在]][[漢]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: shēn zài cáo yíng xīn zài hàn
===Etymology===
From ''[[w:Romance of the Three Kingdoms|Romance of the Three Kingdoms]]''<br>
Literally: ([[w:Guan Yu|Guan Yu]]'s) body is in [[w:Cao Cao|Cao Cao]]'s camp, but his heart is with the [[w:Han Dynasty|Han]]
===Idiom===
# subjugated by one authority, while still remaining loyal to another; not loyal
#: ''[[不少]][[大學生]]'''身在曹營心在漢''' [[剛]][[簽約]][[就]][[想]][[跳槽]]''[http://64.233.167.104/search?q=cache:5yU2vcHdzYoJ:finance.nen.com.cn/74347876758585344/20060227/1857764.shtml+%22%E8%BA%AB%E5%9C%A8%E6%9B%B9%E8%90%A5%E5%BF%83%E5%9C%A8%E6%B1%89%22+site:.cn&hl=zh-CN&gl=cn&ct=clnk&cd=20]
#: ''A growing number of university graduates are '''not loyal''' to their employers; Right after they've signed a contract of employment, they're already thinking of jumping ship''

